headline: Rio Grande LNG Train 5 Secures Enough Buyers to Reach FID
summary: 'NextDecade has now announced a total of 4.5 MMtpa of LNG from train V sold under 20-year LNG SPAs, which it believes is sufficient to support a positive FID on train V'.
